{"tid":2380862,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 大摩憂行業競爭大 續唱淡吉利僅睇8元","createTime":"2021-01-26T07:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T10:59:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"941425b7f04dfa19cc32f0b0ad5227cba007a5d6","tid":2380862,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T07:42:35.000Z","msg":"目標價：8元 (較前收市價15.64元有48.9%潛在跌幅)<br />\n<br />\n吉利公布中期業績後，摩根士丹利發表報告，擔心行業競爭大，吉利或需減價應戰，故將睇淡前景。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，吉利上半年平均售價按年下跌6%至7.1萬元人民幣，毛利率下滑0.7個點子至17.1%。雖然管理層估計今年內地汽車銷售跌一成，同時也降今年銷售目標至132萬輛，但由於下半年會推出新車，相信該銷售目標可以完成。<br />\n<br />\n大摩認為，吉利估值仍高，因之前公布回歸科創板後推高股價，隨著內地行業競爭大，吉利大有機會再減售價，重申「減持」評級，目標價僅睇8元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/stock/article/2555457\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fstock%2Farticle%2F2555457&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=d0a53480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/stock/article/2555457</a>"},{"pid":"c81678ad65237a299b1548463a8b17015c499a8a","tid":2380862,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T07:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9fbfe53c320c925ee2267f19d9cd5d0cae01e4","tid":2380862,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T07:43:28.000Z","msg":"drop to $0 soon"},{"pid":"875eef10f965b6c08343c00e14a5c8ace524d40e","tid":2380862,"uid":99355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T07:46:08.000Z","msg":"2020年8月， 上一頁，完。"},{"pid":"73cc23fd3e33cab52be4b5a32c0a11331dc2af1e","tid":